    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>Tamuz 8th 5614</date> AM.</p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>July 4th</date>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><addressee>Revd. Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>!</p>
            <p rend="align(center)">Dear Sir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Enclosed you will find two dollars for the Occi-<lb/>dent; but
                strange I did not receive one No. since <date>Oct.</date><lb/> last and No. <hi
                    rend="underline"><date><sic>Novembre</sic> 1853</date>
                    <date>Jan. 1854</date>
                    <date>Feb.</date>
                    <date>Mrch</date>
                    <date>Apr.</date>
                    <date>May</date>, <date>June</date> &amp; <date>July</date></hi><lb/> I miss;
                consequently am short of these Nos. in order to make<lb/> the volume complete; as I
                file them; since I am a sub,<lb/>scriber. Please forward them to me to my annexed
                re-<lb/>siding place; but it is time enough, if you send them, when<lb/> the next
                No. is issued. You will oblige me also by in-<lb/>serting my marriage Notice in your
                next No. (which is enclosed)<lb/> and <sic>chrge</sic> the same to my a/c. With the
                compliance of<lb/> these requests, I shall feel under many obligations</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">to you Yours Resp.</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">Solomon Weil</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>No. 469 Eight Avenue</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>between 34th &amp; 35th Str.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>P. S. If you deem it proper—I have visit the place &amp; got all these<lb/>
                informations, from the Sect. <persName>Mr. Cohen</persName>—who is my Bro. in Law—to
                insert<lb/> the enclosed in your valuable Periodical, resp. <placeName>Newark N.
                    J.</placeName> it shall be to your disposition.</p>
        </body>
